lines.text: if you live the life you please

waiting for someone to tell you everything
sit around & wonder what tomorrow will bring

if you've got someone to love

just glad to be here happy to be alive
and it don't matter if by my side
even if you're old and grey
you still got something to say
best you can do is forgive
if you live the life you please
even if the sun don't shine
were going to the end of the line
